Media Query : 
-------------
1. Media Query is mainly used to make webpage responsive
2. Its a key feature of CSS
3. We can make web page responsive in several mode like portrait, landscape and on any specific width.
4. We need to use @media key to define media query in our webpage
5.  Syntax : 
    @media screen | all | print | speech and (max-width:360px){
        ...
        ...
    } 

    @media screen | all | print | speech and (min-width:360px){
        ...
        ...
    } 

    @media screen | all | print | speech and (orientation:portrait){
        ...
        ...
    } 

    @media screen | all | print | speech and (orientation:landscape){
        ...
        ...
    } 